Final Page UIStep 5: Run the Application
Finally, start your local server:
npm run devClick the Login button, and you will be seamlessly redirected to the Asgardeo login page. Once authenticated, you will be redirected back to your app, where your profile details will be displayed!
Conclusion
Integrating enterprise-grade security into a React application doesn’t have to be complicated. With WSO2 Asgardeo and its React SDK, we managed to set up a secure authentication flow in just a few minutes.
You can find the complete source code for this project on my GitHub here: https://github.com/krishan-gif/wso2-asgardeo-react-app
Happy Coding!
